Package: cloudflare-ddns
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: dynamically change a DNS record using Cloudflare
 This is a oneshot tool: you run it, it updates the DNS record, and terminates.
 To make it run periodically you can use a systemd timer.
